WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:02.700
Is one of them alright?

2
00:00:02.866 --> 00:00:05.566
I'm fine, sorry mom

3
00:00:05.866 --> 00:00:07.466
I've got you worried again.

4
00:00:07.466 --> 00:00:09.766
Silly boy, what are you apologizing to your mother for?

5
00:00:09.766 --> 00:00:12.100
Do you have anything to say to mom?

6
00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:13.766
I want to ask you

7
00:00:14.066 --> 00:00:17.433
Have I lost my memory?

8
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.600
Why do you suddenly ask that?

9
00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:24.800
Images have been running through my head lately.

10
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:26.466
What's the picture?

11
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:30.066
I saw that I married Han Chuan

12
00:00:30.366 --> 00:00:32.300
But I cry a lot

13
00:00:32.300 --> 00:00:35.566
She got really sick and died.

